Smiley Face Cursor. Replaces default cursor with a cute smiley face cursor. Change the usual mouse pointer to an amazing custom cursor.
Cute smiley face cursor is a wonderful extension for anyone who wants to change the default mouse pointer to a cute and fun one. The cursor opens a new tab with a search bar. Search features are provided by Microsoft Bing. No changes to your browser default search settings will be made.
By installing the Smiley Face Cursor extension, you agree to the the Privacy Policy elaborated on Horizon Group website:
Privacy Policy: https://horizon-grp.com/?page_id=3
The icons are Royalty Free.
